:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4cb8d6b2032c1b8a8c58678af7a118e212485ad","tid":2246224,"uid":121021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T15:27:00.000Z","msg":"曼谷示威晚上和平散去 警方沒有干預<br />\n<br />\n泰國曼谷連續第四日有反政府示威，數以千計示威者星期六在曼谷街頭抗議。警方沒有干預，示威者晚上和平散去。當局下午封閉市內多個鐵路站，阻止示威進行。有今日上街市民說，不滿警方出動水砲車，批評當局做法過份，行出來參與是要向政府展示實力。穿著黑色上衣的示威者，高叫要求總理巴育下台的口號。巴育已經表明不會辭職。防暴警察昨晚開水炮，驅散佔據道路的示威者。<br />\n<br />\n2020-10-17 23:00:19<br />\n今晚竟然和平散去"},{"pid":"608c1b2423dd257d1b56564a18e8d1bf032e4da6","tid":2246224,"uid":121021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T15:44:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f939d72b41b16a09abb5f0b737f2315c248150","tid":2246224,"uid":121021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T16:10:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/appear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/appear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065024058cd197cc7ca96018d35560f211ab2cb7","tid":2246224,"uid":121021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T16:39:20.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"a10643419232eb444beb7c185c9b1baae3f91152","tid":2246224,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T16:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69e72e62a2a23e3d8ed9349a0d004b5abbb3f28b","tid":2246224,"uid":121021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T16:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eead08a9f530d54fcd8ce9a041d387d7b43180fc","tid":2246224,"uid":121021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:13:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif